room_title: Escape room "Dauntless Kingdom" by Race to Escape in Tampa
room_address: 2435 US Highway 19 N Suite 101 Holiday, FL 34691
room_description: It's 1400 AC you travel to England to the place called the dauntless kingdom known for its strength in hopes to unite. When you arrive you enter the throne and suddenly realize you have been sealed in the room with no one in sight. There are noises of the dragon coming from the dungeon room next to you. Panic sets in! Is there a way out? Do you have what it takes to slay the dragon, find the King and restore the city ... Or better yet... Save yourself? Are you dauntless or fainthearted?
